{"tid":1510274,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"新鴻基 創意提醒：不該掉進馬桶的3樣東西","createTime":"2019-08-27T06:26:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T15:35:32.000Z","uid":207634,"like":191,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"27aa2324d7dd02e8ba4bdda9d1196a220d79b7b3","tid":1510274,"uid":207634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:26:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.homesquare.com.hk/zh-hant/node/158\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.homesquare.com.hk%2Fzh-hant%2Fnode%2F158&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi2ipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=919506f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.homesquare.com.hk/zh-hant/node/158</a><br />\n<br />\n不該掉進馬桶的3樣東西<br />\n<br />\n為什麼前人分別發明了垃圾桶和馬桶？明顯是兩者有著不同的任務。身體的廢物，生活的廢物，各有自己該消失的空間。別以為水聲一沖，所有廢物都能從眼前消失，若把以下物品掉進馬桶裡，只會造成淤塞。<br />\n<br />\n1)    牙線<br />\n<br />\n看似微不足道的牙線，卻不能被生物分解，換句話說，就是不會融解並積聚在水管中。日積月累，糾纏成難以處理的線團。以後每天用完牙線過後，便好好地把它掉進垃圾桶中吧。<br />\n<br />\n2)  任何帶油脂的食物<br />\n<br />\n吃不完的餸菜，杯麵的餘湯，把它們倒進馬桶大概是很多人的習慣。但是，這其實不恰當。遲日一天會讓馬桶產生異味，還會造成渠管淤塞。正確的處理方法是在廚所放置一個大型密實袋，把所有的油脂也倒進去，滿了就扔掉。密實袋能防止異味散開，不用擔心。<br />\n<br />\n3)  膠布<br />\n<br />\n洗澡前摵去的膠布應該掉去哪裡？小心一點，膠布與牙線一樣不能被生物分解，也會造成渠管淤塞。即使是紗布也不應掉進馬桶，好好的把它放到垃圾桶吧。"},{"pid":"31f48c7f57f6f7accfcc3852f2138603a4093e64","tid":1510274,"uid":33930,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:26:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi2ipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=f1db7936\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi2ipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=98db2c9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi2ipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=6fdbc15f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"ce30e2bfea60ba4266b7e9790842ee0a460ef969","tid":1510274,"uid":258566,"like":13,"dislike":12,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:27:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa72cf7efef90d5911821cfe9a51ff8224510f91","tid":1510274,"uid":218215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:28:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bea62bc65169165b4b4467d2835c8beaaf899867","tid":1510274,"uid":69472,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:37:02.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc5d184f24ff0453412488df0ae0a5eb7b034682","tid":1510274,"uid":305843,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:40:01.000Z","msg":"可以係邊度做"},{"pid":"1027a9491597acb574be31decf48376f7d54fd5c","tid":1510274,"uid":36612,"like":101,"dislike":1,"score":100,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:48:12.000Z","msg":"低層啲住客條渠有機會比依啲野塞左會搞到倒灌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申試過"},{"pid":"d451f2c04c00d8d1f4e7a53775434976ee2b1ead","tid":1510274,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:49:43.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"e9f2ad7f0fcf2455930a8dd62e37d570505e9841","tid":1510274,"uid":105353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:53:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb4c13e4767bc26